Immolator- (5)
- Starts with 0% heat.
- When attacked, the attack is negated, unless it's an unstoppable attack, but it adds 40% heat. 
- During the night, immolator can gain 25% heat to perform a weak attack at a target OR gain 25% heat to weak protect any teammate for a night.
- When not attacked, immolator loses 5% heat at the start of night and 10% heat at the start of day.
- Immediately dies when reaching 100% or more heat. When respawned, it starts again with 0% heat.
- Respawns in 6 phases.
